Youcca Troubetzkoy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Youcca_Troubetzkoy 0 Youcca Troubetzkoy (Russian: Ю́рий Никола́евич Трубецко́й; December 12, 1905 – April 22, 1992), also credited as Youcca Troubetzkov and Nicolas Barclay, was a French-American actor.He was member of the princely Trubetskoy family, son of Prince Nikolai Nikolaievich Troubetzkoy (1867–1949) and the countess Jekaterina Mikhailovna Mussin-Pushkin (1884–1972). His brother, Prince Igor Nikolayevich Troubetzkoy (1912–2008) became a race car driver.
